  <!-- EN: charge lance rifle -->
  <RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.label>冲锋枪</RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.label>
  <!-- EN: An ergonomic pulse-charged rail-assisted lance rifle. Fires a three-round burst shot at high velocity, charging them with unstable energy as they leave the acceleration rail. Less accurate compared to a single shot, the intention is to intimidate as much as it is to maim. -->
  <RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.description>符合人体工程学的脉冲充能轨道辅助长矛步枪。可高速发射三发连发子弹，并在子弹离开加速轨道时充入不稳定能量。与单发步枪相比，该枪的精度较低，其目的既是恐吓，也是致残。</RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.description>
  <RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.tools.barrel.label>桶</RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.tools.barrel.label>
  <RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>冲锋枪</RM_Gun_ChargeLanceRifle.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  <!-- EN: charge pistol -->
  <RM_Gun_ChargePistol.label>冲锋枪</RM_Gun_ChargePistol.label>
  <!-- EN: A charged-shot burst-fire sidearm. Pulse-charge technology charges each shot with unstable energy as it leaves the barrel. Released on impact, the charged energy greatly increases the damage done.\n\nDesigned as a sidearm for infantry mechanoids with manipulators similar to human hands. The attached blade gives it superior melee viability. -->
  <RM_Gun_ChargePistol.description>充能连发狙击步枪。脉冲充电技术可在每一发子弹离开枪管时为其注入不稳定的能量。在撞击时释放，带电能量会大大增加造成的伤害。

设计用于步兵机械人的随身武器，其操纵器与人类的手类似。附带的刀片使其具有更强的近战能力。</RM_Gun_ChargePistol.description>
  <RM_Gun_ChargePistol.tools.barrel.label>桶</RM_Gun_ChargePistol.tools.barrel.label>
