  <!-- EN: inferno launcher -->
  <RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.label>地狱发射器</RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.label>
  <!-- EN: A portable version of the Inferno cannon, this fires smaller incendiary warheads. While capable of putting out a burst of four shells, this also means that it suffers in terms of range and accuracy compared to the original. The entire front casing has been weakened to handle multiple shells, weakening the weapon as a whole.\n\nDesigned as a support weapon for infantry mechanoids with manipulators similar to human hands, however they are incredibly cumbersome. -->
  <RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.description>地狱加农炮的便携版，可发射较小的燃烧弹头。虽然可以发射四发炮弹，但这也意味着它在射程和精确度方面都比原版要差。为了应对多发炮弹，整个前部外壳都被削弱，从而削弱了武器的整体性能。

该武器被设计为步兵机械人的辅助武器，具有类似人类双手的操纵器，但却非常笨重。</RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.description>
  <RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.tools.stock.label>库存</RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.tools.stock.label>
  <RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.tools.barrel.label>桶</RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.tools.barrel.label>
  <RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>地狱发射器</RM_Gun_InfernoLauncher.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  <!-- EN: inferno rifle -->
  <RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.label>地狱步枪</RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.label>
  <!-- EN: A portable version of the Inferno cannon, this fires smaller incendiary warheads. While it can fire more rapidly thanks to less recoil, this also means that it suffers in terms of range and accuracy compared to the original.\n\nDesigned as a support weapon for infantry mechanoids with manipulators similar to human hands, however they are quite cumbersome. -->
  <RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.description>地狱加农炮的便携版，可发射较小的燃烧弹头。由于后坐力较小，它的发射速度更快，但这也意味着它在射程和精确度方面比原版要差。

它被设计为步兵机械人的辅助武器，具有类似于人类双手的操纵器，但相当笨重。</RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.description>
  <RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.tools.stock.label>库存</RM_Gun_InfernoRifle.tools.stock.label>
